Programming languages which are used for Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence projects
Python - works with frameworks - NumPy, SciPy and Pandas. Easier to find appropriate developer.
R - the most popular language for machine learning, for large-scale data-mining, visualization and reporting. 
MATLAB/Octave - for representing and working with matrices.
Java -  only for implementing critical enterprise software systems
C/C++ - for low-level software, also for embedded projects (automotive, IoT, etc)
